---
<section id="servicos" class="px-6 py-20 md:px-12 md:py-[120px]">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-[1240px]">
    <div class="mb-14 flex flex-wrap items-end justify-between gap-6" data-aos="fade-up">
      <div>
        <span class="text-[13px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.08em] text-primary">O que fazemos</span>
        <h2 class="mt-3.5 font-display text-[28px] font-bold tracking-[-0.02em] text-[oklch(16%_0.02_250)] md:text-[38px]">Dois jeitos de acelerar seu negócio.</h2>
      </div>
      <p class="m-0 max-w-[360px] text-[15.5px] leading-[1.55] text-[oklch(42%_0.012_250)]">Cada projeto é desenhado do zero pro que sua empresa realmente precisa — nada de pacote fechado.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-7 md:grid-cols-2">
      <div class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-[20px] bg-secondary p-8 md:-translate-y-3.5 md:p-11" data-aos="fade-up">
        <div class="absolute -right-10 -top-10 h-40 w-40 rounded-full bg-[oklch(56%_0.19_258_/_0.18)]"></div>
        <div class="relative z-10 mb-6 flex h-[52px] w-[52px] items-center justify-center rounded-[14px] bg-primary">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><rect x="3" y="4" width="18" height="14" rx="2" stroke="white" stroke-width="1.7"/><path d="M3 8h18" stroke="white" stroke-width="1.7"/><path d="M8 21h8M12 18v3" stroke="white" stroke-width="1.7" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="relative z-10 mb-2.5 font-display text-2xl font-bold text-white">Landing Pages &amp; Sites</h3>
        <p class="relative z-10 mb-6 max-w-[380px] text-[15px] leading-[1.6] text-[oklch(80%_0.01_250)]">Sites rápidos, responsivos e construídos com SEO desde a fundação — feitos pra converter, não só pra existir.</p>
        <div class="relative z-10 flex flex-col gap-3">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2.5"><span class="text-base text-[oklch(70%_0.16_258)]">✓</span><span class="text-[14.5px] text-[oklch(88%_0.008_250)]">Design responsivo, mobile-first</span></div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2.5"><span class="text-base text-[oklch(70%_0.16_258)]">✓</span><span class="text-[14.5px] text-[oklch(88%_0.008_250)]">Otimizado pra aparecer no Google</span></div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2.5"><span class="text-base text-[oklch(70%_0.16_258)]">✓</span><span class="text-[14.5px] text-[oklch(88%_0.008_250)]">Focado em conversão real</span></div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="rounded-[20px] border border-[oklch(90%_0.006_250)] bg-white p-8 shadow-[0_20px_40px_-24px_oklch(20%_0.02_250_/_0.15)] md:p-11" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="80">
        <div class="mb-6 flex h-[52px] w-[52px] items-center justify-center rounded-[14px] bg-[oklch(94%_0.03_258)]">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3" stroke="oklch(45% 0.18 258)" stroke-width="1.7"/><path d="M12 2v3M12 19v3M4.2 4.2l2.1 2.1M17.7 17.7l2.1 2.1M2 12h3M19 12h3M4.2 19.8l2.1-2.1M17.7 6.3l2.1-2.1" stroke="oklch(45% 0.18 258)" stroke-width="1.7" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="mb-2.5 font-display text-2xl font-bold text-[oklch(16%_0.02_250)]">Sistemas Personalizados</h3>
        <p class="mb-6 max-w-[380px] text-[15px] leading-[1.6] text-[oklch(42%_0.012_250)]">Ferramentas sob encomenda que automatizam o processo específico da sua operação — não um software genérico.</p>
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-3">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2.5"><span class="text-base text-primary">✓</span><span class="text-[14.5px] text-[oklch(30%_0.01_250)]">Feito sob medida pro seu processo</span></div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2.5"><span class="text-base text-primary">✓</span><span class="text-[14.5px] text-[oklch(30%_0.01_250)]">Elimina tarefas manuais e repetitivas</span></div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2.5"><span class="text-base text-primary">✓</span><span class="text-[14.5px] text-[oklch(30%_0.01_250)]">Escala junto com sua empresa</span></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
